                            "name": "Two Actions"
                        },
                        "text": "The reborn devotee makes four stalk Strikes at a \u20132 penalty, each against a different target. These attacks count toward the reborn devotee's multiple attack penalty, but the multiple attack penalty doesn't increase until after it makes all its attacks."
                    }
